{"title":"AMS drops Hasie “Ideas Machine” NFT to match mud guard, frame protection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ams-drops-hasie-ideas-machine-nft-to-match-mud-guard-frame-protection/","date":1639771436000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div data-off-canvas-content=\"\"><main><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145215/ams-hasie-and-the-robots-ideas-machine-nft.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"511\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145215/ams-hasie-and-the-robots-ideas-machine-nft-800x511.jpg\" alt=\"ideas machine NFT from Hasie and the Robots and All Mountain Style\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145215/ams-hasie-and-the-robots-ideas-machine-nft-800x511.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145215/ams-hasie-and-the-robots-ideas-machine-nft-297x190.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145215/ams-hasie-and-the-robots-ideas-machine-nft-120x77.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145215/ams-hasie-and-the-robots-ideas-machine-nft-768x491.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145215/ams-hasie-and-the-robots-ideas-machine-nft.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></main><main role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-281189\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Last year’s Hasie &amp; The Robots collection from All Mountain Style showcased&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hasiecustoms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">artist Johan Johnston’s</a> work on their <a href=\"https://www.allmountainstyle.com/collections/ams-x-hasie-the-robots/products/ams-x-hasie-the-robots-frame-guard-extra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">frame protection decals</a> and <a href=\"https://www.allmountainstyle.com/collections/ams-x-hasie-the-robots/products/ams-x-hasie-the-robots-mud-guard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mud guard</a>, and now they’re dialing up the color with an animated NFT to match.</p><p>The project is an extremely limited edition giveaway, with just 10 total NFTs being minted, and only five going to customers…for now. Four are reserved for their team and the artist, and one’s being saved to do something cool with later. The other five will go to randomly drawn names from everyone who signs up as interested. <a href=\"https://www.allmountainstyle.com/pages/ideas-machine-by-hasie-the-robots-x-ams-genesis-nft\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">More details on their website</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders.jpg\" alt=\"hasie and the robots all mountain style frame protection and mud guard for mtb\" width=\"1600\" height=\"894\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders-297x166.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders-800x447.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders-120x67.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders-768x429.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/17145217/ams-hasie-collection-mtb-frame-guard-fenders-1536x858.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>AMS’ co-founder told us it’s really just for fun, they wanted to show off the art and do something special for their fans and customers. They’ll airdrop the NFT to the winners’ wallets for free, without gas fees. Check out <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xA57C9596934591c69bF720EdB988555F7522d2F7/1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the official animated NFT on OpenSea</a>.</p><p>All Mountain Style is also a supporter of <a href=\"http://www.bikeclub.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bike Club NFT</a>, the world’s first blockchain-based cycling club that mints in early 2022 (<em>full disclosure, I’m a partner on that project, and you can read <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bike-club-nft-is-the-first-blockchain-based-cycling-club-to-be-minting-real-world-benefits/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zach’s story about Bike Club here</a></em>).</p><p><a href=\"https://www.allmountainstyle.com/pages/ideas-machine-by-hasie-the-robots-x-ams-genesis-nft\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>AllMountainStyle.com</em></a></p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"1d74005af14f5bc590d86a5725f0d5d3a76f9191a380c55943e9ea5718b20244","category":"Cycling"}